title: iCIMS Holiday Party 2015
desc: The holidays will soon be here, Our yearly party, too. Let's gather 'round and spread some cheer, With all our iCIMS crew. Come one, come all, you folks in red, To one amazing fair. You'll be so thrilled (and nicely fed!), We hope to see you there. Colin cordially invites you and a guest to join us for the iCIMS 2015 Holiday Party! Friday, December 18, 2015 7:00 p.m. to 11:00 p.m. Addison Park 150 Highway 35  Aberdeen, NJ Interested in hotel accommodations at our corporate rate? Contact  Cristy Ziegler , Event Associate, for more information.
